The Portuguese agent has, however, ruled out a move to Real Madrid becuase Karim Benzema is still the main striker at the Bernabeu.  

'Falcao will play for one of the seven best [teams] in the world next, but Real Madrid have Benzema.'

Mendes also revealed that Portugal defender Pepe is set to stay at Real, despite reports linking him with a January move.

'He is staying at Real Madrid. Last season the president could have sold him and he didn't,' said Mendes.

 

